===Head toward the Skysplitter's lower deck to speak with the player from the Yaoqing{{subst:void|<!--401540401-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Skysplitter|Lovers of "Pathfinder" took advantage of the Wardance excitement and organized a large-scale event on the Skysplitter. It wouldn't hurt to see what it's about.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}

;(Talk to Chess Fan From Yaoqing)
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' {{Size|28|(Trailblazer), please wait a moment!}}
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' You're finally here! Oh, you don't know how long I've been waiting for this! So, when shall we start?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Huh? Who are you?
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Me? I'm just your average "Pathfinder" enthusiast. My name won't ring a bell with most people. You, on the other hand, are a legend in the community!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You know me?
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' You're a big name in the community. Everyone that plays "Pathfinder" recognizes you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Start? Start what?
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Oh, you're such a jokester, (Trailblazer). I'm talking about "Pathfinder," of course! Nobody else in the Xianzhou plays it better than you, after all.
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Wait... Don't tell me that guy from the Divination Commission didn't tell you about our event?
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Sheesh, I gave him a pass for being bad at chess, but he can't even do this simple task, right? I'm kicking him from the community when I get back.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He told me, but I forgot about it.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He didn't tell me anything.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You folks bully people in your community?
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' My apologies for the mix-up. As amends, why don't I introduce the event to you again?
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Those of us in the community may think the world of "Pathfinder" as a game, but if you look at the gaming market as a whole, you'll find that "Pathfinder" ultimately remains a niche game. Why do you think that is?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Because it's too easy.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Impossible! Did Hexanexus raise their difficulty? They're attracting more players than us.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Because the community atmosphere is poor.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' This is a mind-training game. People always say, "Those with high IQs have low EQs." We are a high-IQ gaming community, so of course the atmosphere would suck.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The players suck at the game.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' You shouldn't make such a bold claim! It's important to reflect on ourselves more and not blame players when we aren't making good games!
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' But the crux of the problem is that the community lacks an opinion leader. If you look at ''Celestial Jade'', you'll see that Qingque is their role model for the average person working a wage.
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' What about ''Aetherium Wars''? Well, they have Silver Wolf. As someone wanted by the IPC, her name is known across the cosmos &mdash; even if it's in infamy.
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' But ''"Pathfinder"''? We don't even have a single prominent player to our name, except for...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...The Chess Ghost.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Heliobi? Just forget about 'em! Don't let the iron fist of the Ten-Lords Commission chew us out again...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...You.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Me? Haha, I'm not even important enough to have an actual name.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Except me.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' I like geniuses with self-awareness like you.
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' It's you! The fearless Trailblazer, the fame-forgoing altruistic Nameless, the batter who shakes the cosmos, and the custodian of urban cleanliness!
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' In short, you're the "Pathfinder" community's only hope. If you play Pathfinder in a busy place like the Skysplitter, you're sure to draw attention to the game.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sorry, but my match is about to start.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's too embarrassing to play in front of so many people.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's in it for me?
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Wait, don't be so hasty. Now, if you'll look over here...
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' It isn't much, but they're all yours once the deed is done.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are we waiting for? Let's get started.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What a ruthless gambit. I can't say no now, can I?
:'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' Let me know when you're ready. I'll set up the chessboard for you.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm ready.
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I need a moment to get ready.
::'''Chess Fan From Yaoqing:''' I'll be waiting for you here with the chest.
::{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

