:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm not the best player?
::'''Chess Fan From Fanghu:''' Regrettably, a player from the Zhuming whose skills are comparable to yours will also be participating this time. However, I'm confident that you'll take the top spot once you can solve this game I've set up.
:'''Chess Fan From Fanghu:''' Ah, but I digress. Shall we start the game?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm ready.
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I need a moment to get ready.
::'''Chess Fan From Fanghu:''' Sure. The title of Grandmaster will always be here for the taking.
{{Dialogue End}}

