;(Talk to Chess Fan From Zhuming)
:'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' (Trailblazer)! Where do you think you're going? Come and face me! We'll see which one of us is more qualified to lead the "Pathfinder" community.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I wasn't going anywhere.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why are you yelling?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is everyone in the community this high-strung?
:'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' For three centuries have I dominated the Pathfinder community, trouncing more opponents than hairs have fallen off my scalp. Yet here you are, a young upstart trying to steal my thunder!
:'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Do you truly believe yourself qualified to lead the community just because you lucked out and won a few chess games?
:'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Hmph! You'd best remember this: If you lose to me today, you're forbidden from ever playing "Pathfinder" again.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What if I win?
::'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Hah, that will never happen.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I don't even want to play.
::'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Why, you little... You'd blaspheme against our greatest, most sacred, and most delightful "Pathfinder"!? Mark my words: I shall see you utterly defeated today!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll win this game. I want that chest!
::'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' You're playing for such a contemptible reason? I knew you weren't worthy of being our thought leader!
:'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Alright, let's cut the chatter. Prepare yourself for judgment!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Bring it on.
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I need a moment to get ready.
::'''Chess Fan From Zhuming:''' Hah, prepare all you want, but you'll never win.
